Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.60,0:01:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,As a doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.20,0:01:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,As a man...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.90,0:02:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.87,0:02:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba Ryo,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.64,0:02:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,have you really come to terms with such fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.08,0:02:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.48,0:02:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,are you really the man \NDaiba Ryo would put his life on the line for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.19,0:02:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(900,900)\an8\c&HFBFDFE&\bord0\shad3\blur0.5\4c&H696256&\b1\fnHitch Hike\fs45\4a&H00&}Episode 16\N {\fs100}\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\NSworn  Friend 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.40,0:02:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Good heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.60,0:02:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Aside from mayonnaise, \Nthere's nothing but some sprouted onion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.21,0:02:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayonnaise it is then.{unsure, maybe it's "should I eat onion that gave shoots in mayonnaise or just mayonnaise?"}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.68,0:02:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.48,0:02:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.01,0:02:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.22,0:02:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What brings you here at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.09,0:02:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, nothing special.{/wanted to hang out/for a bit, I thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.89,0:02:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,How about that? \NWanna join me for a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.29,0:02:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Most certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.76,0:03:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I barged in completely uninvited{/all of a sudden}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.60,0:03:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, without a supply of foods, \NI'd be in much more trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.94,0:03:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.34,0:03:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,To the meeting.{guess, he says "first of all" or "for the moment" none of which makes sense}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.45,0:03:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How times flies...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.68,0:03:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You still remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.32,0:03:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Our first ever battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.42,0:03:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember it, and vividly at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.82,0:03:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Of all places, \NI'd never expect Oumi to show up in Slothium{/to meet ...}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.26,0:03:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.10,0:03:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, relax and take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I am going to inspect your condition thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.63,0:03:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it! You have a volvulus!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.31,0:03:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How can that be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.61,0:03:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, I'm on the my way to losing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's the perfect way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.75,0:03:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,'Tis was one good battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.79,0:03:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That naive boy then, \Nnow you are a Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.19,0:04:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It was but a stroke of luck then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.39,0:04:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You really think nothing but luck is involved?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.03,0:04:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, what I'm talking about is not the battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.56,0:04:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.57,0:04:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,About what a luck it has been for me \Nto meet Daiba and Oumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.47,0:04:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I believe \Nyou're thus obliquely confessing your love?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.17,0:04:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the hell did you get that idea?{I never said anything to point to that!}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.08,0:04:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess not. \NJokes aside, though,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.41,0:04:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya, actually, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nevermind...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.92,0:04:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You are even weirder than usual today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.29,0:04:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.86,0:04:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,keep fighting in Slothium?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.43,0:04:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why?{\i0} \NWell, about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.60,0:04:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You do it to fight Daiba Ryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's why \Nyou also need to hurry the hell up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have as much time \Nas you'd probably like to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.91,0:04:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Had it not been for my rivalry with Oumi, \Nthere wouldn't have been current me{/I could only make it to this day thanks to ...}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.88,0:04:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I should probably be upfront{/he uses this special word reserved for confessions of one's feelings} with you \Nand say thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.11,0:04:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.95,0:05:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought, \Nit's a love confession after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times do I have to say it's not!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.59,0:05:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya's path{/aim} lies towards the world \Nfar beyond my scope{/the reach of my hand}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.72,0:05:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep on growing{/maturing} \Nat the most unimaginable rate, Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So much, it even spurred Daiba \Nto put his own life on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.23,0:05:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I daresay he made fighting Ginya \Nhis raison d'être.{/Lit: I wonder if he has the desire to fight ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:05:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They gravitate to each other, \Nthough each one only attracts another in order to fight him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.87,0:06:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like they pull one another{added} { manually}\Nby reeling in{half-guess} the {red }thread{/string} of fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.11,0:06:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya is like a carp trying to climb up a waterfall, \Nbeyond which is the promised land.{absolutely hate this line, it's a very convoluted proverb that means roughly "he is a carp/love/dragon(if I got that hinative explanation right) aiming to breach through the gates to success(also has word for dragon inside it)" and with an underlying parable of said carp evolving into a dragon at some point; because it's a rather serious moment I can't even wrap this into a pun damnit}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.38,0:06:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But to do that, he has to turn into a dragon.{no clue what he really says, sounds a bit like "but just a bit, look up" or rather "however, a complete change iragenabara"}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.92,0:06:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Only by fueling it with his own life, \NDaiba Ryo manages to keep that fire going.{/by burning his life ... can sustain that power/maintain ... strengh}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.53,0:06:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I will hardly ever rise to either of their roles.{/I cannot become either of them/will never be able to understand ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.02,0:06:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive! \NHe is trouncing him hard{one-sided isn't it}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Otonashi Ginya again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:06:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since he became a Knight, \Nhis games become less and less a hit or miss{/he shows an ever-increasing tendency for stability}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.47,0:07:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If this keeps up, he'll approach the Generals \Nbefore you can say Jack Robinson{/no telling if he won't be fighting ... in no time}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.67,0:07:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You are indeed less hit-or-miss now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.74,0:07:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.32,0:07:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It is apparent that you lack any ferocity...{/the feeling of fighting desperately for your life}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.82,0:07:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This overwhelming power \Nthat Daiba Ryo endows himself with by burning his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.72,0:07:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.23,0:07:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If this keeps on, Daiba Ryo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.57,0:07:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No, if this keeps up, you may not even get to him,{\there's no guarantee you even arrive there/reach him after a struggle} \Nleave alone defeating{added}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,For Daiba Ryo and Ginya to have an ultimate{/bring to life their} showdown,\NGinya will have to sweep through the General ranks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.68,0:07:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And to do that, \Nhe cannot afford getting defeated even once now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.65,0:07:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Ginya really the receiver of Daiba Ryo's, \Nthe Ultimate King's heritage, of his whole life?{lit: is ... really something like vessel(guess) Daiba bets his life on?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.33,0:07:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.82,0:08:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,can you really dash{/rush/climb/run uphill} all the way up to Daiba Ryo's spot \Nwithout even once being stopped in your tracks?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. \NI have to take the initiative{/ascertain/look to make sure} myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,For me, getting even close to{/becoming like} either Ginya \Nor Daiba Ryo is out of question.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.22,0:08:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Still,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.56,0:08:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,if I manage to show him \Neven a fraction of Daiba Ryo's soul,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll learn to detach from everything{guess: https://jisho.org/word/%E5%89%8A%E3%81%8E%E8%90%BD%E3%81%A8%E3%81%99}, \Nhe'll learn to fight with everything on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.70,0:08:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be able to teach{/pass to/convey to/propagate} him that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.05,0:10:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.80,0:10:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.80,0:10:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing, customer is king.{/you're welcome}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.91,0:10:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.44,0:10:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something stick to my face?{I think it's reference to Yuri's phrase from ep14}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that is not exactly the case.{/nothing of the kind}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Still weird.{guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.41,0:11:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Master is always this way, \Nso we'll let it slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.08,0:11:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And you always feel \Nlike blurting some impertinence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.62,0:11:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up finishing{ eating}.{/It's getting cold}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.18,0:11:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I should{/it is}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.63,0:11:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahoy, Oumi. \NBeen a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.73,0:11:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And what was it that made you pull \Nsuch intimidating a face?{/And what brought you here with such scary looks?}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.83,0:11:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.74,0:11:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya, I need to engage \Nin a conversation with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.18,0:11:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with the formal{/ceremonial} demeanor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.78,0:11:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.55,0:11:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first time I'm seeing Oumi \Nwith that kind of expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.13,0:11:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.59,0:11:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask you to fight me.{I want a battle with you - accent on battle as some violent bout}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.11,0:12:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.41,0:12:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? \NThat fighting thing or that demand for answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.21,0:12:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.08,0:12:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you. \NI accept.{/Let's meet in a fight. (guess)}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.62,0:12:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight, at 12PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.99,0:12:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the place.{/I'll be waiting here.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.36,0:12:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.77,0:12:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world has gotten into Oumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.71,0:12:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.65,0:12:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he ate something weird again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.72,0:12:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Something weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a lunch box far behind expiry date.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.72,0:12:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Suit yourself.{guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.53,0:12:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all as Yuri says.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.72,0:13:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the damn is he thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Kept you waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.17,0:13:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.25,0:13:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A dedicated parlor just for us, huh?{/without anyone}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.52,0:13:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A little favor from an old acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.65,0:13:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Just for today, it's all ours{/I borrowed it}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.99,0:14:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, it changes the mood{/atmosphere/vibe} completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.26,0:14:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.29,0:14:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I have already chosen the machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.30,0:14:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have even conditions.{/same}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.66,0:14:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.40,0:14:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,chances are, this would make \Na concluding{final} battle between me and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.73,0:14:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight I'm throwing my everything at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.31,0:14:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, Ginya,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to fight at earnest too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.50,0:14:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Start.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.94,0:14:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me. Even if you'll think of me as a brute,{/even if it's too harsh/sever} \NI intend to push you to the edge.{/stomp you; it's https://jisho.org/search/muri but I dunno how to handle it, maybe "I go all out on you"}{ today}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.66,0:15:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!{/THere!}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.57,0:15:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Though we're just getting started, \Nyou nailed jackpot already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.81,0:16:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oumi is not being his usual self. \NHe dropped any foreplay, proceeding straight to palpation.{/He barely introduced himself and started palpating on the onset}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.31,0:16:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, his threat{guess - daito} earlier \Nand this self-exhausting manner of pressing the buttons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.64,0:16:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's almost like...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.12,0:16:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,he is fighting the God of Death{/death} himself!{I guess it's just a terribly stupid line, but it very much sounds like a reference or another folklore story}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.26,0:16:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. But you're not in perfect health{guess, maybe "you're not good to go yet"} yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.43,0:16:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All right... \NThat's a good child.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.90,0:16:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.30,0:16:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Riichi Eyes? Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.70,0:16:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever! I can do it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.54,0:16:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, Riichi Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There! Nailed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... That's the way, Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.46,0:16:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.95,0:16:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.06,0:16:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.33,0:16:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We're amidst the fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.43,0:16:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Not some frivolous frolic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:16:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember what I said?{/should have said - no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.23,0:17:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm throwing my everything at you, \Nfight me at earnest!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.77,0:17:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this pressure... \NWhat in the world has gotten into Oumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.74,0:17:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{Return to the/}Resume the play,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.78,0:17:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.63,0:17:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This kind of pressure. \NWhere have I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.61,0:17:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba Ryo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.07,0:17:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same as when I fought Daiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.39,0:18:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one thing I need to pass to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,0:18:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I am absolutely obliged to pass this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.74,0:18:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be growing all the stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.31,0:18:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The fight you found yourself in\Nis a challenge to the dream!{this sounds awful but I'm at the end of my wits}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.88,0:18:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The fight with your everything on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.88,0:18:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If you allow yourself to even think of losing to me now, \Na dream of challenging Daiba Ryo will remain a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe!{unsure, maybee "I believe"}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.35,0:18:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You are still to become much stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My everything... on the line...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.19,0:18:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.40,0:18:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This kind of magnificent fight
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.07,0:18:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,is not something one can devise on the whim.{/Lit: is not something you can do even if you want to}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.31,0:18:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything I have, I will throw it at Oumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.69,0:19:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what Ginya ought to do. \NThat's what Daiba Ryo's rival ought to do!{/Lit: that's why ginya... that's why he is daiba ryo's rival}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.98,0:19:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.61,0:19:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it was me \Nwho learned{/gained} the most from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.88,0:19:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.42,0:19:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'm free of any afterthoughts and regrets.{/I don't have any regrets about this}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.42,0:19:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I will file in the resignation from Slothium.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.62,0:19:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But why...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.89,0:19:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe when you rise to a Knight... \NNo, to a General!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.89,0:19:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to. \NIt's settled already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.70,0:19:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.17,0:19:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.77,0:19:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I will say it just once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.47,0:19:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.91,0:20:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you lose, Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.62,0:20:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dash through every obstacle \Nstraight up to Daiba Ryo's spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.25,0:20:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,For the moment, \Nhe is still second in my list of targets.{I'm clueless as to what is mada here - still or more or at least - nothing makes sense here; would assume he refers to Oumi as "I should defeat that person now" but why tf he says now and not before that}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.76,0:20:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.69,0:20:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds so much like you.{WHY THE FUCK}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.50,0:20:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no longer any time to loiter{/you cannot allow yourself to stay still idly/leasurely/resting anymore}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.24,0:20:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope I conveyed to you all that I intended to.{PURE FUCKING GUESS, what the fuck is even this "koko no namae/kokoro ga mae" - nothing makes sense, not even the clear part of "*something* wo up to telling *affirmating da*"}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.97,0:20:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, one way or another, do your best from now on. \NIn my stead too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.98,0:20:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.69,0:20:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take it seriously{do it for me}, Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.46,0:20:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The time left \Nis considerably less than what you'd like to have.{The time left for you is shrinking to a measly span.}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.06,0:22:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,To come.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.80,0:22:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,To not come.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.67,0:22:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Phone.{guess, no one watches jikai anyway}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.81,0:22:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.07,0:22:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.68,0:22:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.08,0:22:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Person on my Mind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.78,0:22:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My finger will stop the time.
